=== SIGNATURE ===
exists(arr, value)
=== COMMENT ===
Checks whether value is present anywhere in arr; returns 1 or 0.
=== CODE ===
=LAMBDA(Arr, Val, IF(ISNUMBER(XMATCH(Val, TOCOL(Arr), 0)), 1, 0))
=== DESCRIPTION ===
Membership test: is a value present in an array.

Arguments:
  arr   - array to search (flattened before testing).
  value - the scalar value to look for.

Returns:
  1 if value occurs in arr, otherwise 0.

Example:
  exists(list, "x")  ->  1
